{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "D'abord, commen\u00e7ons par", "start": 0.233, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "dire qu'aujourd'hui,", "start": 0.916, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "nous maltraitons nos professeurs,", "start": 1.883, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "depuis bien trop longtemps,", "start": 3.383, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "et toutes les familles politiques", "start": 4.583, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "qui ont gouvern\u00e9", "start": 6.0, "duration": 0.533}, {"text": "ont leur responsabilit\u00e9 l\u00e0-dedans.", "start": 6.533, "duration": 1.833}, {"text": "Quand on commen\u00e7ait comme prof\u2019", "start": 8.366, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "dans les ann\u00e9es 80,", "start": 10.066, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "on commen\u00e7ait avec l'\u00e9quivalent", "start": 11.566, "duration": 1.684}, {"text": "de deux Smic.", "start": 13.25, "duration": 0.783}, {"text": "Aujourd'hui 1,2 Smic.", "start": 14.033, "duration": 1.883}, {"text": "Un professeur qui commen\u00e7ait", "start": 15.916, "duration": 1.834}, {"text": "dans les ann\u00e9es 80", "start": 17.75, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "pour acheter un appartement", "start": 18.833, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "de 80 m\u00e8tres carr\u00e9s \u00e0 Paris,", "start": 20.1, "duration": 1.816}, {"text": "il avait besoin", "start": 21.916, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "- c'est Marianne", "start": 22.75, "duration": 0.55}, {"text": "qui avait fait cette \u00e9tude ", "start": 23.3, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "- de huit ans de salaire.", "start": 24.6, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "Aujourd'hui, 40 ans de salaire.", "start": 25.1, "duration": 1.616}, {"text": "Et la v\u00e9rit\u00e9,", "start": 26.716, "duration": 0.517}, {"text": "c'est que cette faiblesse", "start": 27.233, "duration": 1.717}, {"text": "de la r\u00e9mun\u00e9ration,", "start": 28.95, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "qui est aussi visible", "start": 29.7, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "dans les comparaisons internationales,", "start": 30.533, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "elle va avec le d\u00e9classement", "start": 32.1, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "du m\u00e9tier d'enseignant.", "start": 33.5, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "Elle va avec le m\u00e9pris", "start": 34.583, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "que, d'une certaine mani\u00e8re,", "start": 35.966, "duration": 1.834}, {"text": "les autorit\u00e9s, pendant trop longtemps,", "start": 37.8, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "les gouvernements successifs,", "start": 39.566, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "mais aussi la soci\u00e9t\u00e9 fran\u00e7aise", "start": 40.7, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "peut-\u00eatre, a t\u00e9moign\u00e9 envers ceux", "start": 41.9, "duration": 1.416}, {"text": "qui ont pourtant", "start": 43.316, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "la mission la plus fondamentale,", "start": 44.216, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "celle de pr\u00e9parer notre avenir.", "start": 45.766, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "On parle tellement peu d'\u00e9cole !", "start": 47.333, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "Et au-del\u00e0\nde la question du salaire des profs,", "start": 48.9, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "moi je voudrais dire", "start": 50.433, "duration": 0.583}, {"text": "\u00e0 tous les professeurs", "start": 51.016, "duration": 0.734}, {"text": "qui exercent", "start": 51.75, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "le m\u00e9tier que j'ai exerc\u00e9", "start": 52.766, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "pendant dix ans, et que j'esp\u00e8re", "start": 53.9, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "retrouver bient\u00f4t,", "start": 54.866, "duration": 1.25}, {"text": "je voudrais leur dire \u00e0 quel point,", "start": 56.116, "duration": 2.05}, {"text": "aujourd'hui, ils doivent \u00eatre", "start": 58.166, "duration": 2.517}, {"text": "l'objet d'une reconnaissance", "start": 61.95, "duration": 1.966}, {"text": "de la nation", "start": 63.916, "duration": 1.034}, {"text": "pour le travail", "start": 64.95, "duration": 0.616}, {"text": "qu'ils font, envers et contre tout,", "start": 65.566, "duration": 1.984}, {"text": "parfois dans un sentiment d'absurdit\u00e9,", "start": 67.55, "duration": 1.916}, {"text": "de d\u00e9couragement,", "start": 69.466, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "qui atteint des sommets.", "start": 70.616, "duration": 1.617}, {"text": "Quand on pense que", "start": 72.233, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "cette augmentation...", "start": 72.866, "duration": 0.584}, {"text": "Pardon, mais l\u00e0", "start": 73.45, "duration": 0.916}, {"text": "il y a une vraie violence :", "start": 74.366, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "elle est en partie conditionn\u00e9e", "start": 75.5, "duration": 2.016}, {"text": "\u00e0 l'adh\u00e9sion \u00e0 un pacte,", "start": 77.516, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "qui va faire que les professeurs", "start": 79.283, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "vont travailler plus.", "start": 80.366, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "Dans quel m\u00e9tier on dit aux gens :", "start": 81.666, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": "\u201cvous \u00eates beaucoup moins pay\u00e9s que la moyenne,", "start": 83.866, "duration": 1.684}, {"text": "il faut un rattrapage salarial,", "start": 85.55, "duration": 1.45}, {"text": "mais on le fera \u00e0 condition", "start": 87.0, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "que vous fassiez", "start": 88.7, "duration": 0.716}, {"text": "des t\u00e2ches suppl\u00e9mentaires.\u201d", "start": 89.416, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "Donc vous \u00eates oppos\u00e9", "start": 90.15, "duration": 0.766}, {"text": "\u00e0 cette partie de l'augmentation.", "start": 90.916, "duration": 2.684}, {"text": "Il y a le socle, qui sera de 5.5%, et", "start": 93.6, "duration": 2.033}, {"text": "ensuite le pacte ?", "start": 95.633, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "Non, mais d'abord le pacte...", "start": 96.65, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "Pardon, mais c'est un nouvel \u00e9pisode", "start": 97.883, "duration": 2.317}, {"text": "de l'Absurdistan", "start": 100.2, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "administratif fran\u00e7ais.", "start": 101.033, "duration": 2.017}, {"text": "Alors vous allez", "start": 103.05, "duration": 0.35}, {"text": "devoir signer un pacte,", "start": 103.4, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "mais vous pourrez signer un demi-pacte,", "start": 104.55, "duration": 1.583}, {"text": "disait le ministre", "start": 106.133, "duration": 0.817}, {"text": "il y a quelques semaines.", "start": 106.95, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "Peut-\u00eatre un pacte et demi...", "start": 107.9, "duration": 1.466}, {"text": "Enfin tout \u00e7a n'a aucun sens...", "start": 109.366, "duration": 1.784}]}